---
import CvtLayout from "../../layouts/CvtLayout.astro";
---

<CvtLayout title="Vision — CVT" description="Why trust infrastructure matters for Uganda, Africa, and informal economies.">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6">
    <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-400">Vision</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 font-display text-4xl font-semibold text-white">Why trust infrastructure matters</h1>

    <div class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-slate-300">
      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-white">Informal economies</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">Most commercial mobility in Uganda runs on relationships — SACCOs, stages, word of mouth. That works locally but does not scale to insurers, national employers, or cross-border logistics. Trust infrastructure turns verified facts into portable standing.</p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-white">Uganda & Africa</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">CVT is designed for Ugandan registration realities: NIN-linked identity, category-specific verification, and channels people already use (WhatsApp, mobile web). The model extends across Africa where informal work dominates and credit bureaus reach only a fraction of the economy.</p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-white">Insurance before credit</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">Trust Profile v1 emphasises insurer-grade signals — active insurance, training, clean moderated record — before any CRB or credit-mix integration. Insurance unlocks mobility risk pooling; credit is a separate, regulated programme for v5+.</p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-white">Long-term vision</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">What LinkedIn did for formal employment networks, CVT can do for mobility and commercial operators: a verified registry, a timeline of facts, and consent-gated sharing with partners — with rehabilitation built in so complaints do not permanently destroy reputations.</p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-4 border-t border-white/10 pt-8">
      <a href="/cvt/map" class="rounded-full border border-white/20 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm text-slate-200 hover:bg-white/5">Project map</a>
      <a href="/cvt/roadmap" class="rounded-full bg-teal-600 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-teal-500">Implementation roadmap</a>
      <a href="/cvt/docs/vision" class="rounded-full border border-white/20 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm text-slate-200 hover:bg-white/5">Full vision doc</a>
      <a href="/cvt/concepts" class="rounded-full border border-white/20 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm text-slate-200 hover:bg-white/5">Explore concepts</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</CvtLayout>

<style>.font-display { font-family: "Fraunces", Georgia, serif; }</style>
